Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,RUNNING TOWARDS THE DREAM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie was walking for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal to fall after\Nwalking all this distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It lost all its energy after it returned to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, do you think Lassie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it came from Scotland up to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to recover slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie did all this for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we'll take\NLassie to John's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you carry Lassie home, Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, here is your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, sleep peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't send you anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For this you shall rest assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After it sleeps well, it will reactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, we have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It returned after walking 600 miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an unreasonable distance for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It returned and it completely\Ndestroyed his hair and body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfaher, are you still thinking\Nabout taking Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean that the dog's hair\Nwas affected by rain and mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to say it is a great dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- We go too!\N- Take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It sleeps deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His body is tired so it\Nmay not walk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,John, breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I change my clothes now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still sleeping on the kitchen floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you slept well, Lassie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, it's breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Its body is too tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so it can't eat by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll feed you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It slept again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels comfortable when it is on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It woke up, but it was hard for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It should get well slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But his ear was completely destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a travel badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, but this is very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In this way the rich man Rudling will not\Nput eyes on him, and he will keep them shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the shape at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is important is to be with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Try a little more, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie... you're gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon you can travel anywhere you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye! Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It started eating as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty the Duke of Rudling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Majesty Duke Rudling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, you seem to have revived the mine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as a miracle, and was about to close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...this was not my achievement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of a boy and his dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That dog is a Collie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to have happened very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Are you a journalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm from the London Journal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is possible to tell us about\Nthe cause of this miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,until we publish his command in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it should not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It deserves praise from all people directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that the music\Nyou play draws a xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the fullest of the sky\Nlike the winds of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So put your hand on your chest and be brave!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, my heart, I'm happy to be lonely!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all for this lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important not to forget your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have walked all this distance\Nand you aren't tired to meet me, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes to you in the after noon\Nevery day at the three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just heard about Lassie's story\Nfrom the Duke of Rudling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- xxx\N- You, can you look here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to smile again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's great, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will be a very wonderful story!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The boy who reopened the mine!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the miracle dog who\Ntraveled a long journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why we have to publish\Nthis story in our newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, can I talk to you a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After work I bought it from\Nthe Jones' store but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, my father is weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose the things you always love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, in this newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John and Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dog Lassie ​​walked 600 miles to John,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after a long reunion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have become well known in England!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this from everyone to Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After the British newspaper article,\NLassie became very impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I first receive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,mail of this size at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you came back early today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want another article to be written.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many journalists from\Nmultiple companies coming to the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You say Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the future of this dog is\Ndifferent from the rest of the dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Besides, didn't it do something similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When Dr. Hooper fell in the abyss,\Nit told us to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, tell us more about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't evade work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh...\N- We want to talk to you for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in your clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And even in the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything to the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hooper told me not to intrude\N"Don't enter the clinic"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about John?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He has gone with Priscilla and others to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And also Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, John? It has become\Na modern newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become famous, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not, Lassie is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we get to this area,\Nno one will reach us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- Rock Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Lassie is in good health,\Nthen we can go up together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. McNeill...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Actually I'm a journalist,\Nso finding this place is simple for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I want to invite you,\NJohn with Lassie to a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- A party?\N- A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is your and your friends\Nsecret rock castle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you climb to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm busy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's people's messages to Lassie\Nafter they read the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of Lassie, I will read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who who?\N- Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it audacious to read\Nthe messages of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes! I apologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not our companion as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will he stay in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,T-t-this message!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...! Wait a moment, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel nostalgic, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It''s a message from someone\Nwho met Lassie on its journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To my dear Purcell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, actually your name is Lassie, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dan went out to the village to sell the eggs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He brought with him that newspaper.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I expected, you returned after a long wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You also had a precious family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We haven't mistaken to send you to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you returned you were finally happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am also very happy for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greetings to your precious family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nice message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, you met many people on your trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One day I want to thank them with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it happy that I wrote\Nabout Lassie in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Approximately...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the concert is held!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These... on what occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke Rudling said
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he would organize a concert marking\Nthe miraculous journey of Lassie,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would be praised there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the villagers will be invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... can you call
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the old couple at the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can attend the concert together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, as or the concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,please keep it secret from\Nthe rest of the journalists!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our library will work on exclusive coverage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end we couldn't climb the peak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although Priscilla had trouble coming here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The preparation of the day\Nwas strictly confidential!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is thanks to John and Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything ready, McNeil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,John and the miners are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,will appeal to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now I'll look at the equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who made the journalists do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all the hype!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that I thought of myself only,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and put John and Lassie under\Nthe pressure of many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I make him trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey you have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you work on our star for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This child is not nice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I wear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke Rudling has invited many\Npeople with high positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You will become an apprentice\Nif you appear on your nature, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my usual look really pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a motive so strong that\Nthe mine is not closed because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No adult can do what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Duke of Rudling admire you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we want to\Nshow you in the finest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to think that this\Nwill  make your future better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be treated in this\Nceremony as an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This clothes will not make you\Njump and play in the fields!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I rely on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It will change your mindset when\Nit takes you a beautiful picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sir McNeill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still want something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, will Grandpa Dan\Nand Grandma and Dili really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's concert will highlight the elderly\Ncouple who helped to reunite Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they seem to be a little late! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it will not go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is decorated in the next room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Decorated?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The next is to brush off your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,These devices will add an amazing effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to pay attention to the guests now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our sales this time will be better\Nbecause our material is full of tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm glad to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the Duke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All seem to have high positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone came because of what they\Nread about Lassie in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is excited about John's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you can wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took a long time because of your ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't it nice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to have started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When your turn comes I will tell you,\Nwait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't like this shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They exaggerated our form, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In some way, I feel that it is completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who found coal,\Nand Lassie faced death on its way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of Lassie's long journey\Nwas full of misfortunes and fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The basis of it was his separation from John
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but John...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For Greenor Bridge he swore that coal\Nwould come out with all the power he had!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said: Lassie! Sorry I can't come\Nback to you, with tears in his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take full responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,John was very sure he would\Nextract coal for the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was here that Lassie decided\Nto return to whatever the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me introduce to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle dog Lassie, and its owner John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They have not yet appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually this message...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Duke of Rudling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still unable to enter the world of adults.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still want to run with Lassie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the others in the fields!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize to everyone, despite the fact\Nthat they have struggled to come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,John Carraclough...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Remy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm not alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I have a lot of nice friends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, where is my mother?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"HOMELESS GIRL REMY"\NPlease look forward!{\i0}
